### Phase 2 — Implementation & First Test (fast, creative)
I’ll produce:
- **Posting Engine** – possibly mixing unexpected posting slots, repost patterns, or “dark” posts in private groups.  
- **DM Delivery** – creative triggers beyond just comments (e.g., profile visits, reactions) if tools allow.  
- **Retargeting** – not only ads; could include partner email swaps, remarketing via unrelated channels (e.g., podcasts).  
